quran[7{c,v,t}:
39,41,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) hum ne sab insanon ke liye yeh kitaab brhq tum par nazil kar di hai ab jo seedha rasta ikhtiyar kere ga apne liye kere ga aur jo bhatkay ga uss ke bhatakne ka wabaal usi par hoga, tum unn ke zimma daar nahi ho"
39,42,"woh Allah hi hai jo mout ke waqt roohein qabz karta hai aur jo abhi nahi mra hai uss ki rooh neend mein qabz kar laita hai, phir jis par woh mout ka faisla nafiz karta hai ussay rok laita hai aur dosaron ki roohein aik waqt muqarrar ke liye wapas bhaij deta hai iss mein barri nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karne walay hain"
39,43,"kya uss khuda ko chore kar inn logon ne dosaron ko Shafi bana rakha hai? un se kaho, kya woh Shafaat karen ge khuwa unn ke ikhtiyar mein kuch nah ho aur woh samajte bhi nah hon ?"
39,44,"kaho, Shafaat saari ki saari Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hai asmano aur zameen ki badshahi ka wohi maalik hai phir usi ki taraf tum pulta-ay jaane walay ho"
39,45,"jab akailey Allah ka zikar kya jata hai to akhirat par imaan nah rakhnay walon ke dil krhhne lagtay hain, aur jab uss ke siwa dosaron ka zikar hota hai to yakayak woh khusi se khil uthte hain"
39,46,"kaho, khudaaya! asmano aur zameen ke peda karne walay, haazir o gayab ke jan-nay walay, to hi apne bundon ke darmain uss cheez ka faisla kere ga jis mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain"
39,47,"agar inn zaalmon ke paas zameen ki saari doulat bhi ho, aur itni hi aur bhi, to yeh roz qayamat ke buray azaab se bachney ke liye sab kuch فدیے mein dainay ke liye tayyar ho jayen ge wahan Allah ki taraf se un ke samnay woh kuch aeye ga jis ka unhon ne kabhi andaza hi nahi kya hai"
